snippet.title: UK: Amber Heard calls Depp libel trial "incredibly painful" in statement after closing arguments
snippet.description:
Subscribe to our channel! rupt.ly/subscribe

Actor Johnny Depp's ex-wife, actress Amber Heard gave a statement outside The Royal Courts of Justice on the day of the closing  in Depp's libel trial against The Sun newspaper in London on Tuesday. 

Depp brought the lawsuit against the publication over a 2018 article claiming he was abusive to Heard. She has testified in defence of the publisher, speaking about the occasions in which she alleges Depp attacked or threatened to kill her.
